OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FApart from the odd shower in
OL,6,Fthe east this morning it will be a dry
OL,7,Fday. Variable amounts of cloud and
OL,8,Fsome bright or sunny spells.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry but
OL,11,Fclouding over. Outbreaks of rain will
OL,12,Fspread south for a time overnight
OL,13,Ffollowed by a dry end to the night.
OL,14,FCold.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,17,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,18,Fsome sunny intervals. Rather cold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
