OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FEarly
OL,6,Frain on Tuesday then sunny spells and
OL,7,Fshowers. Remaining unsettled Wednesday
OL,8,Fand Thursday with scattered showers.
OL,9,FChance of overnight frost.
